reviews.text:
Bagel Bagels everywhere! This is a great bagel place/cafe. They offer bagels, sandwiches and soup. Very large, lots of tables, chairs, lounge area with a small TV and a conference room too. 
Semi-handicapped. There is a small step in front.
Good Bagels. Good coffees. Good teas.  Great place to chill, read, and enjoy.....👍👍
Try their Gravlax, you will not be disappointed.

Great homemade bagel shop in Wakefield. I had an egg sandwich and everything was very fresh and delicious. They also have a cold brewed ice coffee which was great. Large place on the inside with plenty of seating if you were looking to meet with someone or just relax. Recommended if you are in the area. Also easy off from the highway.
Nice local place. Clean, simple furnishings. Limited menu but good fresh baked goods. No complaints.
